text: int main ( ) { int t ; long long int divisor , dividend , a , b , product , rem ; scanf ( "%d" , & t ) ; while ( t -- ) { scanf ( "%lld%lld" , & a , & b ) ; product = a * b ; if ( a > b ) { divisor = b ; dividend = a ; } else { divisor = a ; dividend = b ; } while ( divisor ) { rem = dividend % divisor ; dividend = divisor ; divisor = rem ; } printf ( "%lld %lld\n" , dividend , product / dividend ) ; } return 0 ; }
